Extract unique labels from an atlas

Source: R/atlas-utils.R
atlas_labels.Rd

Extract unique labels from an atlas

Usage

atlas_labels(x)

brain_labels(x)

Arguments

x

brain atlas

Value

Character vector of atlas region labels

Examples
